Metric: Monthly Recurring Revenue
Description: Sum of normalized monthly subscription fees from all active paying customers. Annual plans are divided by 12. Excludes one-time charges, usage overages, and free trials.
Owner: finance-analytics
Tags: mrr, revenue, saas, subscription, executive-kpi

Source: subscriptions, invoices

Given the subscription status is "active" or "past_due"
  And the subscription has a paid plan (not free or trial)
  And the billing interval is monthly or annual

When we calculate
  Then sum the recurring charge amount for each active subscription
  And normalize annual subscriptions by dividing by 12
  And exclude any one-time add-on charges or usage overages

The result is "Monthly Recurring Revenue"

Trust:
  Freshness must be less than 4 hours
  Null rate on plan_amount must be less than 0%
  Null rate on billing_interval must be less than 0%
  Row count of subscriptions must not drop more than 5% day over day
  Value must be between 5000 and 10000000
  Value must not change more than 20% month over month
